&lt;p&gt;This is a remote sales position for candidates located in South Carolina, preferably in the Charleston area. &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;#LI-SOUTHCAROLINA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
