&lt;li&gt;Natural critical-thinking and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent writing and editing skills with a keen attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intuition for marketing, someone who loves thinking about what gets a concept to really click for a consumer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in Excel and Google Sheets, especially Pivot tables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go-getter mindset, proactive and driven&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creativity and curiosity&lt;/li&gt;
