&lt;p&gt;IXL Learning, a developer of personalized learning products used by millions of people globally, is seeking a District Partnership Specialist to join our Professional Learning team and support districts in Ohio. &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;#LI-EM1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
